data.description: Discover the ideal family oasis in this inviting multi-level home. Boasting a thoughtfully designed layout, this residence offers the perfect blend of functionality and comfort. The upper level showcases 3 spacious bedrooms, providing both privacy and convenience. Enjoy abundant natural light and energy efficiency thanks to newer windows and siding. Entertaining is a breeze with a generously sized deck, an ideal setting for gatherings and outdoor enjoyment. Stay cozy during the colder months by the warm fireplace, creating a perfect ambiance for relaxation. This home also features a newer furnace, with the AC unit being replaced in 2022 to ensure comfort and peace of mind year-round. Nestled in a serene and private backyard, you can escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life. Whether you're starting a family or seeking a tranquil retreat, this multi-level gem offers it all. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream home, where convenience and charm converge seamlessly.
